{"tid":2323633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[蒙住面都知咩人]男子在警車前搶劫計程車，國外網友封「史上最蠢搶匪」","createTime":"2020-12-13T10:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T10:39:35.000Z","uid":188176,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9651400a2267577375b3dc5d53ca36dbd289772","tid":2323633,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:15:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CCyvqchLksE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCCyvqchLksE&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=33f58dcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CCyvqchLksE</a><br />\n<br />\n美國有個搶匪趁司機停等紅燈時搶劫計程車，但歹徒竟然沒發現後面就停著一輛警車，結果搶到一半就被後方的員警制伏，被國外鄉民封為「史上最蠢搶匪」<br />\n<br />\n詳細事件經過及後續：<br />\n影片中的搶匪是18歲的Victor Martinez-Herrera，他那天坐上計程車司機Ralph Valletta的車，趁著停等紅燈的時候進行搶劫，害怕的司機交出身上僅有的11塊美金，但搶匪沒注意到後面就停著一輛警車，結果號誌轉為綠燈時，計程車依然沒有動靜，後方的員警Terry Ely發覺有異下車查看，過程中仔細聆聽兩人的對話，聽到司機求搶匪「不要對他開槍」，於是他馬上上前逮捕搶匪。<br />\n<br />\n後來該名被搶的司機回想當時經過，因為太過緊張感覺心臟非常不舒服，他受訪時表示如果警察再晚一點出現，他肯定會心臟病發。而搶匪Victor Martinez-Herrera則被以搶劫、恐嚇以及傷害等罪起訴，目前被羈押在伯克郡監獄等待判決。"},{"pid":"848c9dfa61841bc1e1b7919070c1d16a886b936f","tid":2323633,"uid":16057,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:16:00.000Z","msg":"又笑鳩啲...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nYou&rsquo;re racist"},{"pid":"ef8470b8e7b77064e56c55ed01242253f8a0bd02","tid":2323633,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b11b2ac38ddac2d63503f1bdc14149d19ed47f6","tid":2323633,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:17:24.000Z","msg":"GTA警車前面搶車即刻一星"},{"pid":"f2ce006900413d4068ced545cbf28f94fd9817b3","tid":2323633,"uid":188176